title: Annoying Questionary v1.1
description:
Annoying Questionary

Is a Pop-Up program who show every minute a random question.
The Pop-Up is always in the middle and always on top.
The user of the has to answare the question with a good answare,
If the answare is false the Pop-Up will not close.
When the user has the right answare the PopUp will close and in a minute there will be another question.

When the user think i will restart windows, the Pop-Up will be there again (How Annoying).
When you start the program 'Annoying Questionary - Remover.exe' Then the program is removed from the pc with no damage at all to the pc.

How to use it:
* Run the file 'Annoying Questionary v1.1.exe' you will see nothing, but after 1 minute there will be your first question.
* Run the file 'Annoying Questionary - Remover.exe' to get rid of this annoying program.


Changelog:
